INSERT INTO `plants` VALUES (1,1,'OLKARIA I','Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.',1,'2020-01-01 00:00:00','2020-01-01 00:00:00'),(2,1,'OLKARIA II','',1,'2020-01-01 00:00:00','2020-01-01 00:00:00'),(3,1,'OLKARIA IV','<p>TThe Olkaria 280MW project comprises the Olkaria IV and the Olkaria I units 4 and 5 each with a capacity of 140MW.In 1999, KenGen drilled exploratory wells for Olkaria IV geothermal field. The Government of Kenya, in 2006, funded appraisal drilling for this field. Production drilled then commenced in 2007 by signing of six well drilling contract.</p>\n<p>  The company signed a total of six contracts for the drilling of the geothermal wells for this project. In any good geothermal system there is need for both production and reinjection wells. This system is what gives the Olkaria field the capacity to support its plants as the reinjection wells ensures replenish of the field. This project has a total of 52 production wells and 19 reinjection wells.</p>\n<p> Construction works on the 280MW Olkaria geothermal power plant began in March 2012 and on 23rdJuly 2012, His Excellency retired President Hon Mwai Kibaki.</p>\n',1,'2020-01-01 00:00:00','2020-01-01 00:00:00'),(4,1,'OLKARIA V','',1,'2020-01-01 00:00:00','2020-01-01 00:00:00'),(5,1,'WELLHEADS','',1,'2020-01-01 00:00:00','2020-01-01 00:00:00'),(6,1,'WELLHEAD LE','',1,'2020-01-01 00:00:00','2020-01-01 00:00:00'),(7,1,'MODULAR','some description here and there',1,'2020-01-